= Change History

(See log/changelog.txt for full commit log.)

== 0.3.5 / 2007-12-16

* Improved cssfilter.rb; now far enough along to be useful.

== 0.3.4 / 2007-12-14

* Added css.rb and cssfilter.rb. Both are in early developemnt stage.
* Fixed escaping of DesignKit attributes.

== 0.3.3 / 2007-12-05

* Design kit can now add arbitray elements for open elements.
* Improvements to XML Design Kit (API is starting to stablize).
* Improved ATOM feed.

== 0.3.2 / 2007-11-28

* Created XmlDesignKit to facilitate support for a variety of XML formats.
* First format using XmlDesignKit is Atom feeds.

== 0.3.1 / 2007-11-13

* Ported nitro/glue's UriUtils module.
* Ported nitro/raw's atom.rb (but it needs work!)

